author: Jose Martinez
title: Photos Have Surfaced From the Crime Scene of Kim Kardashian’s Paris Robbery
text:
Jose is a contributing writer for Complex Media. @ZayMarty Feb 19, 2017 Tweet Image via Getty/Marc Piasecki French news channel TF1 have released a set of photos pertaining to the armed robbery of Kim Kardashian in Paris last October. The images, obtained by TMZ, give us a glimpse inside Kim's hotel and the surrounding area on the night of the crime, as well as a look at the suspects congregating after the incident. 
Kim Kardashian Robbery Crime Scene Pics Surface (PHOTO GALLERY) https://t.co/MLX3CiqvYA — TMZ (@TMZ) February 19, 2017 The first couple of photos provide a chilling look at Kim's dimly lit hotel room, and the bathroom where she was allegedly forced to go into the bathtub. There are also images of the duct tape used to subdue her as the suspects made away with the jewelry worth an estimated $10 million. Related
